When this option is set to True, the information of the URL additionally configured to the DB_OPEN_CONNECTION profile collected by the agend is displayed.

The URL information is included in the profile information of a transaction in the following form.

DB_OPEN_CONNECTION (jdbc/oracle, jdbc:oracle:thin:@127.0.0.1:1521:xe)


â€»Precautions

As this information uses Connection.getMetaData(), additional information is not collected if JDBC driver does not provide the applicable information.

---

* Default value: false 
* Format: Boolean 
* Restart: Not required
* Related options
    * [enable_jdbc_wrapper](./agentHelp?key=enable_jdbc_wrapper&type=1)
    * [enable_jdbc_vendor_wrapper](./agentHelp?key=enable_jdbc_vendor_wrapper&type=1)
    * [enable_connection_trace](./agentHelp?key=enable_connection_trace&type=1)
* Supported version: 5.0.9
